<ab>Hansen Stainlinger, richter czu Grefemwerd </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Stainlinger, als ir uns auf
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief wider
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt von des Kuczhaubts,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> habe
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die im der Raben Hans,
                                    <add><expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan></add> czu Grefemwerd, für
                        Hansen Streber, auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger, bekumert und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und dünckt uns
                                <expan>ungelimpfliche<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz man also
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> sein habe für den
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, damit er nichts cze schicken hat,
                        bekümern sol. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> Raben Hansen schiken und
                        bestellen wollet, daz er dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Kuczhaubt, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger,
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein habe ledig lasse, als etc. Das
                        wollen wir etc. Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> derselb Raben Hans czu
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> Hansen Streber,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> icht cze sprechen,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wollen wir im
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        vollen gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex>s</expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                        ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <add>derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add> anheim <add>ist</add>, <expan>on
                                gev<ex>er</ex>d.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi ut <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
